{"chapter_number":80,"bismillah_pre":true,"revelation_order":24,"revelation_place":"makkah","name_arabic":"عبس","name_complex":"`Abasa","name_simple":"'Abasa","verses_count":42,"pages":[585,585],"meaning":{"text":"He Frowned","en":"He Frowned","id":"Ia Bermuka Masam"},"verses":[[[1,5759,"80:1","عَبَسَ وَتَوَلَّىٰ",["He frowned and turned (his) back,","Dia (Muhammad) berwajah masam dan berpaling,"],585,30,59,234,null,null],[2,5760,"80:2","أَن جَاءَهُ الْأَعْمَىٰ",["Because there came to him the blind man.","karena seorang buta telah datang kepadanya (Abdullah bin Ummi Maktum)."],585,30,59,234,null,null],[3,5761,"80:3","وَمَا يُدْرِيكَ لَعَلَّهُ يَزَّكَّىٰ",["And what would make you know that he would purify himself,","Dan tahukah engkau (Muhammad) barangkali dia ingin menyucikan dirinya (dari dosa),"],585,30,59,234,null,null],[4,5762,"80:4","أَوْ يَذَّكَّرُ فَتَنفَعَهُ الذِّكْرَىٰ",["Or become reminded so that the reminder should profit him?","atau dia (ingin) mendapatkan pengajaran, yang memberi manfaat kepadanya?"],585,30,59,234,null,null],[5,5763,"80:5","أَمَّا مَنِ اسْتَغْنَىٰ",["As for him who considers himself free from need (of you),","Adapun orang yang merasa dirinya serba cukup (pembesar-pembesar Quraisy),"],585,30,59,234,null,null],[6,5764,"80:6","فَأَنتَ لَهُ تَصَدَّىٰ",["To him do you address yourself.","maka engkau (Muhammad) memberi perhatian kepadanya,"],585,30,59,234,null,null],[7,5765,"80:7","وَمَا عَلَيْكَ أَلَّا يَزَّكَّىٰ",["And no blame is on you if he would not purify himself","padahal tidak ada (cela) atasmu kalau dia tidak menyucikan diri (beriman)."],585,30,59,234,null,null],[8,5766,"80:8","وَأَمَّا مَن جَاءَكَ يَسْعَىٰ",["And as to him who comes to you striving hard,","Dan adapun orang yang datang kepadamu dengan bersegera (untuk mendapatkan pengajaran),"],585,30,59,234,null,null],[9,5767,"80:9","وَهُوَ يَخْشَىٰ",["And he fears,","sedang dia takut (kepada Allah),"],585,30,59,234,null,null],[10,5768,"80:10","فَأَنتَ عَنْهُ تَلَهَّىٰ",["From him will you divert yourself.","engkau (Muhammad) malah mengabaikannya."],585,30,59,234,null,null],[11,5769,"80:11","كَلَّا إِنَّهَا تَذْكِرَةٌ",["Nay! surely it is an admonishment.","Sekali-kali jangan (begitu)! Sungguh, (ajaran-ajaran Allah) itu suatu peringatan,"],585,30,59,234,null,null],[12,5770,"80:12","فَمَن شَاءَ ذَكَرَهُ",["So let him who pleases mind it.","maka barangsiapa menghendaki, tentulah dia akan memperhatikannya,"],585,30,59,234,null,null],[13,5771,"80:13","فِي صُحُفٍ مُّكَرَّمَةٍ",["In honored books,","di dalam kitab-kitab yang dimuliakan (di sisi Allah),"],585,30,59,234,null,null],[14,5772,"80:14","مَّرْفُوعَةٍ مُّطَهَّرَةٍ",["Exalted, purified,","yang ditinggikan (dan) disucikan,"],585,30,59,234,null,null],[15,5773,"80:15","بِأَيْدِي سَفَرَةٍ",["In the hands of scribes","di tangan para utusan (malaikat),"],585,30,59,234,null,null],[16,5774,"80:16","كِرَامٍ بَرَرَةٍ",["Noble, virtuous.","yang mulia lagi berbakti."],585,30,59,234,null,null],[17,5775,"80:17","قُتِلَ الْإِنسَانُ مَا أَكْفَرَهُ",["Cursed be man! how ungrateful is he!","Celakalah manusia! Alangkah kufurnya dia!"],585,30,59,234,null,null],[18,5776,"80:18","مِنْ أَيِّ شَيْءٍ خَلَقَهُ",["Of what thing did He create him?","Dari apakah Dia (Allah) menciptakannya?"],585,30,59,234,null,null],[19,5777,"80:19","مِن نُّطْفَةٍ خَلَقَهُ فَقَدَّرَهُ",["Of a small seed; He created him, then He made him according to a measure,","Dari setetes mani, Dia menciptakannya lalu menentukannya."],585,30,59,234,null,null],[20,5778,"80:20","ثُمَّ السَّبِيلَ يَسَّرَهُ",["Then (as for) the way-- He has made it easy (for him)","Kemudian jalannya Dia mudahkan,"],585,30,59,234,null,null],[21,5779,"80:21","ثُمَّ أَمَاتَهُ فَأَقْبَرَهُ",["Then He causes him to die, then assigns to him a grave,","kemudian Dia mematikannya lalu menguburkannya,"],585,30,59,234,null,null],[22,5780,"80:22","ثُمَّ إِذَا شَاءَ أَنشَرَهُ",["Then when He pleases, He will raise him to life again.","kemudian jika Dia menghendaki, Dia membangkitkannya kembali."],585,30,59,234,null,null],[23,5781,"80:23","كَلَّا لَمَّا يَقْضِ مَا أَمَرَهُ",["Nay; but he has not done what He bade him.","Sekali-kali jangan (begitu)! Dia (manusia) itu belum melaksanakan apa yang Dia (Allah) perintahkan kepadanya."],585,30,59,234,null,null],[24,5782,"80:24","فَلْيَنظُرِ الْإِنسَانُ إِلَىٰ طَعَامِهِ",["Then let man look to his food,","Maka hendaklah manusia itu memperhatikan makanannya."],585,30,59,234,null,null],[25,5783,"80:25","أَنَّا صَبَبْنَا الْمَاءَ صَبًّا",["That We pour down the water, pouring (it) down in abundance,","Kamilah yang telah mencurahkan air melimpah (dari langit),"],585,30,59,234,null,null],[26,5784,"80:26","ثُمَّ شَقَقْنَا الْأَرْضَ شَقًّا",["Then We cleave the earth, cleaving (it) asunder,","kemudian Kami belah bumi dengan sebaik-baiknya,"],585,30,59,234,null,null],[27,5785,"80:27","فَأَنبَتْنَا فِيهَا حَبًّا",["Then We cause to grow therein the grain,","lalu di sana Kami tumbuhkan biji-bijian,"],585,30,59,234,null,null],[28,5786,"80:28","وَعِنَبًا وَقَضْبًا",["And grapes and clover,","dan anggur dan sayur-sayuran,"],585,30,59,234,null,null],[29,5787,"80:29","وَزَيْتُونًا وَنَخْلًا",["And the olive and the palm,","dan zaitun dan pohon kurma,"],585,30,59,234,null,null],[30,5788,"80:30","وَحَدَائِقَ غُلْبًا",["And thick gardens,","dan kebun-kebun (yang) rindang,"],585,30,59,234,null,null],[31,5789,"80:31","وَفَاكِهَةً وَأَبًّا",["And fruits and herbage","dan buah-buahan serta rerumputan."],585,30,59,234,null,null],[32,5790,"80:32","مَّتَاعًا لَّكُمْ وَلِأَنْعَامِكُمْ",["A provision for you and for your cattle.","(Semua itu) untuk kesenanganmu dan untuk hewan-hewan ternakmu."],585,30,59,234,null,null],[33,5791,"80:33","فَإِذَا جَاءَتِ الصَّاخَّةُ",["But when the deafening cry comes,","Maka apabila datang suara yang memekakkan (tiupan sangkakala yang kedua),"],585,30,59,234,null,null],[34,5792,"80:34","يَوْمَ يَفِرُّ الْمَرْءُ مِنْ أَخِيهِ",["The day on which a man shall fly from his brother,","pada hari itu manusia lari dari saudaranya,"],585,30,59,234,null,null],[35,5793,"80:35","وَأُمِّهِ وَأَبِيهِ",["And his mother and his father,","dan dari ibu dan bapaknya,"],585,30,59,234,null,null],[36,5794,"80:36","وَصَاحِبَتِهِ وَبَنِيهِ",["And his spouse and his son--","dan dari istri dan anak-anaknya."],585,30,59,234,null,null],[37,5795,"80:37","لِكُلِّ امْرِئٍ مِّنْهُمْ يَوْمَئِذٍ شَأْنٌ يُغْنِيهِ",["Every man of them shall on that day have an affair which will occupy him.","Setiap orang dari mereka pada hari itu mempunyai urusan yang menyibukkannya."],585,30,59,234,null,null],[38,5796,"80:38","وُجُوهٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ مُّسْفِرَةٌ",["(Many) faces on that day shall be bright,","Pada hari itu ada wajah-wajah yang berseri-seri,"],585,30,59,234,null,null],[39,5797,"80:39","ضَاحِكَةٌ مُّسْتَبْشِرَةٌ",["Laughing, joyous.","tertawa dan gembira ria,"],585,30,59,234,null,null],[40,5798,"80:40","وَوُجُوهٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ عَلَيْهَا غَبَرَةٌ",["And (many) faces on that day, on them shall be dust,","dan pada hari itu ada (pula) wajah-wajah yang tertutup debu (suram),"],585,30,59,234,null,null],[41,5799,"80:41","تَرْهَقُهَا قَتَرَةٌ",["Darkness shall cover them.","tertutup oleh kegelapan (ditimpa kehinaan dan kesusahan)."],585,30,59,234,null,null],[42,5800,"80:42","أُولَٰئِكَ هُمُ الْكَفَرَةُ الْفَجَرَةُ",["These are they who are unbelievers, the wicked.","Mereka itulah orang-orang kafir yang durhaka."],585,30,59,234,null,null]],[[[1,2,585,"&#xfb51;","word","عَبَسَ",["He frowned",""]],[2,2,585,"&#xfb52;","word","وَتَوَلَّىٰ",["and turned away",""]],[3,2,585,"&#xfb53;","end","ﭓ",[null,null]]],[[1,2,585,"&#xfb54;","word","أَنْ",["Because","sesungguhnya"]],[2,2,585,"&#xfb55;","word","جَاءَهُ",["came to him","datang kepadanya"]],[3,2,585,"&#xfb56;","word","الْأَعْمَىٰ",["the blind man","seorang buta"]],[4,2,585,"&#xfb57;","end","ﭗ",[null,null]]],[[1,2,585,"&#xfb58;","word","وَمَا",["But what","dan apakah"]],[2,2,585,"&#xfb59;","word","يُدْرِيكَ",["would make you know","tahukah kamu"]],[3,2,585,"&#xfb5a;